OL,6,CG2009FUKTV Style is rebranded Home.
OL,7,
OL,8,FThe channel's schedule is repositioned
OL,9,Fto focus on home improvement/lifestyle
OL,10,Fand gardening.
OL,11,
OL,12,FIn 2019, the BBC's stake in the channel
OL,13,Fwas bought by UKTV co-owner Discovery
OL,14,FInc - the channel was consequently
OL,15,Frebranded HGTV on 21st January 2020.
